{"tid":1744011,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（家長x小朋友x教育工作者)23/11 保護小朋友遊行","createTime":"2019-11-21T13:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T15:36:08.000Z","uid":285481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72bcdc3ebb4985c4f7f197946bdc82e323a2d860","tid":1744011,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"由六月反送中示威活動至今，警方已承認施放超過10,000發催淚彈。警方甚至喺民居或學校附近施放催淚彈，令到最近有好多小朋友有呼吸道或皮膚疾病。而且有害氣體亦會令市民，小朋友健康受到長遠影響。為咗保護下一代，我哋一班家長決定發起遊行，呼籲教育界及家長帶同小朋友一齊參加！<br />\n<br />\n遊行已獲不反對通知書， 希望各位教育界人士，家長帶埋小朋友一同進場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行日期：23/11(星期六)<br />\n遊行時間：10:00a.m.<br />\n遊行地點：九龍塘沙福道》喇沙小學<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情請入Tg link : <a href=\"https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStopKillingOurKids&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=09848eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QoQb9HF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQoQb9HF.jpg&h=77016b45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywKTDA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywKTDA1.jpg&h=4849dc24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9ihkPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9ihkPn.jpg&h=3381b51e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfwrd9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfwrd9p.jpg&h=a51024b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f16uWnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff16uWnL.jpg&h=3e74391d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8aGNur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8aGNur.jpg&h=fb3ee729&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZzDPHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https